---
title: Harira-Style Lentil Veggie Stew with Spiced Naan Wedges and Feta
description: Inspired by the traditional Moroccan soup, Harira, tonight's recipe combines lentils, Moroccan spices, sweet zucchini and savoury crushed tomatoes for a comforting bowl of goodness. Make sure you wipe the bowl clean with the spiced naan wedges!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-legumes-et-de-lentilles-facon-harira-61506af8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/ragout-de-legumes-et-de-lentilles-facon-harira-620053e6106adc1e3c2b1faa-0a88f16c.pdf
